{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although my mother, born in Slovakia, Czechoslovakia, in Trencin, [BACKROUND NOISE] we could not speak any other languages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- we went to Slovakia in 1938 or '39 to visit her side of the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And although, that family, nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I seen them only once in my life, and I have vivid memories about them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we left Czechoslovakia, that visit after that, I never see them anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we heard during the war that some other atrocity has been done in that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And unfortunately, after the war, none of them appeared anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we-- we presumed that everybody's dead on-- on my mother's side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father's side, we had quite a large family, having four-- three sisters, and-- and him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody had two-- every sister had two children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was about eight cousins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and we kept, more or less-- my father kept the whole family as like a-- like a hen of the little chickens around him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so the whole family consisted about 60, 70 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Unfortunately, out of the 70 people, I was the only one who-- who ventured out of Budapest during the-- the persecution time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they caught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's how I got to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- and my rest of my family went through the war time in Budapest, untouched.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, because I was [SIGHS] a-- a-- a sport-minded person, our-- our relationship was more a cordial, because I mixed with non-Jews very freely, and they accepted me-- what I was and-- and whoever I was.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My recollection of-- of persecution in my childhood was very limited.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I would lie if I would say that I had been harassed or-- or-- or been make too much fun of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
